opensuse:
- PasswordAuthentication yes, PermitRootLogin yes (in /etc/ssh/sshd_config) and then service sshd restart
- dpkg alternative
- service reparse

centos:
- PasswordAuthentication yes, PermitRootLogin yes (in /etc/ssh/sshd_config) and then service sshd restart

alpine:
- PasswordAuthentication yes, PermitRootLogin yes (in /etc/ssh/sshd_config) and then service sshd restart
- install python (apk add python3)
- install lsof (not busybox version) (apk add lsof)